The <var>PORTDIR</var> variable was used to point to the main package repository hosted on the system. It has since been {{Bug|546210|text=deprecated}} in favor of the <code>location</code> attribute (whose default value is {{Path|[[:/usr/portage]]}}) of the Gentoo repository configuration inside {{Path|[[:/etc/portage/repos.conf|/etc/portage/repos.conf]]}}.</onlyinclude>

Текущее значение атрибута <code>location</code> можно получить с помощью [[portageq]]:

{{Cmd|portageq get_repo_path / gentoo|output=<pre>
/usr/portage</pre>}}
